QUESTION:
Write a program to generate the following series – 2, 4, 7, 12, 21…..

Sample Input:
5

Sample Output:
2 4 7 12 21

CODE:
#include<iostream>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int n,n1=2;
    cin>>n;
    cout<<"2 ";
    for(int i=0;i<=n;i++)
    {
        n1=(n1*2)-i;
        cout<<n1<<" ";
    }
}
